"Change Set:		ScamperFixDate:			9 July 2000Author:			Daniel VainsencherFix a walkback when entering a document with no title."!!Scamper methodsFor: 'access' stamp: 'dvf 7/9/2000 01:46'!labelString	"return the title of the current page, or nil if there is none"	document == nil		ifTrue: [ ^'Scamper' ]		ifFalse: [ ^'Scamper: ' , (self document head title ifNil: ['(untitled)']) ]! !